In the outskirts of the Valley Mine Pentatron a giant wasp flew 
overhead looking for some entertainment.  He spotted a smoke stack and 
with curiusity flew into it. 
"Ohhh.. what they keep in here?"  He got his answer as wave of smoke 
came up at him blowing him out of it.  He transformed into robot mode 
caughing.
"Foul tunnel shoot bad cloads at Waspinator!" He complained.
